msgid "Storing Script Objects"
msgstr "存储脚本对象"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:4
msgid ""
"Sometimes you may want to store script objects and use them later, or to "
"implement your own container for script objects. There are some tools "
"provided by asbind20 for storing script objects."
msgstr ""
"有时你可能希望存储脚本对象以便稍后使用，或实现自己的脚本对象容器。asbind20 提"
"供了一些工具用于存储脚本对象。"

