#: ../../doc/container.rst:21
msgid "Policies for how containers deal with the type information."
msgstr "容器如何处理类型信息的策略。"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:0
msgid "Template Parameters"
msgstr "模板参数"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:29
msgid "Sequential Containers"
msgstr "顺序容器"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:31
msgid ""
"``small_vector`` is a sequential container for AngelScript objects with "
"small-size optimization (SSO). It stores a fixed number of elements inline "
"(on the stack) before falling back to heap allocation, similar to how "
"``std::string`` uses SSO for short strings."
msgstr ""
"``small_vector`` 是一个用于 AngelScript 对象的顺序容器，具有小尺寸优化（SSO）"
"功能。它在回退到堆分配之前，会将固定数量的元素内联存储（在栈上），类似于 "
"``std::string`` 对短字符串使用 SSO。"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:36
msgid "Template parameters"
msgstr "模板参数"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:38
msgid ""
"**TypeInfoPolicy** — determines how the element type is derived from the "
"type information. Use ``typeinfo_identity`` when the type info *is* the "
"element type (e.g. ``int``, a registered value class), or "
"``typeinfo_subtype<N>`` when the element is the *N*-th subtype of a template "
"type (e.g. ``array<int>`` → ``typeinfo_subtype<0>``)."
msgstr ""
"**TypeInfoPolicy** — 决定如何从类型信息中派生元素类型。当类型信息*即是*元素类型"
"时（例如 ``int``、已注册的值类），使用 ``typeinfo_identity``；当元素是模板类型的"
"第 *N* 个子类型时（例如 ``array<int>`` → ``typeinfo_subtype<0>``），使用 "
"``typeinfo_subtype<N>``。"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:42
msgid ""
"**StaticCapacityBytes** — inline storage size in bytes. Must be a multiple "
"of ``sizeof(void*)``. Defaults to ``4 * sizeof(void*)``."
msgstr ""
"**StaticCapacityBytes** — 内联存储大小（字节）。必须是 ``sizeof(void*)`` 的倍数。"
"默认为 ``4 * sizeof(void*)``。"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:44
msgid ""
"**Allocator** — allocator for heap-backed storage. Defaults to "
"``script_allocator<void>``, which uses AngelScript's memory API."
msgstr ""
"**Allocator** — 用于堆存储的分配器。默认为 ``script_allocator<void>``，它使用 "
"AngelScript 的内存 API。"

