#: ../../doc/container.rst:63
msgid ""
"Element access returns ``void*`` / ``const void*``. You cast to the concrete "
"type:"
msgstr ""
"元素访问返回 ``void*`` / ``const void*``。您需要将其转换为具体类型："

#: ../../doc/container.rst:73
msgid ""
"The container provides standard ``std::vector``-like modifiers: "
"``push_back``, ``emplace_back``, ``push_back_n``, ``emplace_back_n``, "
"``pop_back``, ``insert``, ``erase``, ``resize``, ``clear``, ``reserve``, "
"``shrink_to_fit``, ``reverse``, and ``assign``."
msgstr ""
"该容器提供了与 ``std::vector`` 类似的标准修改操作：``push_back``、"
"``emplace_back``、``push_back_n``、``emplace_back_n``、``pop_back``、"
"``insert``、``erase``、``resize``、``clear``、``reserve``、``shrink_to_fit``、"
"``reverse`` 和 ``assign``。"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:78
msgid "Iterators"
msgstr "迭代器"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:80
msgid ""
"``const_iterator`` is a random-access iterator that stores an offset into "
"the vector rather than a raw pointer. This makes it safe against "
"reallocation — an invalid iterator from script can be detected by the host "
"without crashing. Dereferencing yields ``const void*`` to the element."
msgstr ""
"``const_iterator`` 是一个随机访问迭代器，它存储的是向量中的偏移量而非原始指针。"
"这使得它在重新分配时是安全的——宿主可以检测到来自脚本的无效迭代器而不会崩溃。"
"解引用产生指向元素的 ``const void*``。"

