msgstr ""
"``visit`` 方法对一系列元素应用访问器，处理类型感知的分派："

#: ../../doc/container.rst:107
msgid "GC integration"
msgstr "GC 集成"

#: ../../doc/container.rst:109
msgid ""
"Call ``enum_refs()`` to enumerate references within the vector to the "
"AngelScript GC. This should be called from the object type's "
"``EnumReferences`` callback."
msgstr ""
"调用 ``enum_refs()`` 来枚举向量中对 AngelScript GC 的引用。这应该在对象类型的 "
"``EnumReferences`` 回调中调用。"

